addBank(string,address,string).notice: Add a new bank to the network

addKYCRequest(string,string).notice: Record a new KYC request on behalf of a customer Bank is the sender of this request

downVoteCustomer(string).notice: Function to add a new down vote for a customer

getBankComplaints(address).notice: View total number of bank complaints

modifyIfBankAllowedToVote(address,bool).notice: Modify if a bank is allowed to vote in the KYC process

removeBank(address).notice: Remove a bank from the network

removeUpVoteCustomer(string).notice: Function to remove an up vote for a customer

reportBank(address).notice: Report a complaint against a bank

upVoteCustomer(string).notice: Function to add a new up vote for a customer
